What you need to know:

Sharks coach William Muluya made his first change of the match four minutes later, Eric Juma being rested for Daglas Mokaya.Mazembe used well his superb dribbling skills and pace to place the match beyond the bankers reach with a beautiful strike in the 67th minute. Otanga had a chance pull one back for the hosts in the 72nd minute, but his shot from outside the box blew over the bar.